        <p>Mercury is a global community of people based on mutual trust and joint efforts to achieve the goals of each participant.</p>
<p>Mercury Global is one of the community projects Mercury, which provides each participant the opportunity to create a basic cash flow, to reach the level of prosperity and to sustain it.</p>
<h1 class="news_title">HOW THE PROJECT WORKS</h1>
<p>Mercury Global takes control of the available funds of participants and redistributes them using a unique formula. Every week a portion of the available funds is distributed among all participants, according to the individual prognosis for each. Every Tuesday all participants may submit requests for funds.</p>
<p>the Basis for the work of the project selected cryptocurrencies, as they show their stability, reliability, and independence for a long time.</p>
<h1 class="news_title">TERMS AND CONDITIONS</h1>
<p>The amount transferred by the participant in the funds management determines his / her individual daily forecast (IDF) and the number of days of activation charges. For each currency these parameters may vary.</p>
<p>Perfect Money (PM). The minimum amount of participation in - 100 PM-USD-daily forecast and the number of days of activation charges for all the amounts the same - 1% daily for 300 days.</p>
<p>Bitcoin: the minimum amount of participation is 0.1 BTC, daily forecast and the number of days of activation charges for all the amounts the same - 1% daily for 300 days.</p>
<p>Ethereum: the minimum amount of participation - 1 ETH daily forecast and the number of days of activation charges for all the amounts the same - 1% daily for 300 days.</p>
<p>Litecon: the minimum amount of participation - 1 LTC daily forecast and the number of days of activation charges for all the amounts the same - 1% daily for 300 days.</p>
<h1 class="news_title">PROGRAMS &quot;Leasing&quot; and &quot;CAR FOR 55%&quot;</h1>
<p>With the power of Mercury Global and our partners who directly provide a service of car leasing, now each participant is available for the purchase of the car on very favorable terms.</p>
<p>These programs are moved to a separate site. Soon there will be a link to it.</p>
<h1 class="news_title">IMPORTANT NOTICE!!!</h1>
<p>Monitoring the exchange rate of Bitcoin in recent years has shown that during times of high volatility and the possibility of a sharp drop, he quickly recovers and preserves the overall growth trend.</p>
<p>However, the risk of a sudden drop of the rate of any cryptocurrency, including Bitcoin, there are Mercury Global does not affect the change of exchange rate of any cryptocurrency and is not responsible for the consequences of such changes.</p>
<p>Mercury Global has no obligation to anyone of the participants and does not guarantee any funds to any of the participants.</p>
<p>For violations of the rules of engagement in the Community, any member may be removed from the project with complete deprivation of the right to participate in the distribution of funds.</p>
<p>Mercury Global reserves the right at any time without notice to change the terms of the project.</p>

    
